title: God Has Great Purpose For Your Life
itunes:title: God Has Great Purpose For Your Life
description:
You have everything you need to make a difference in this world. By using your talents and gifts to honor God, you’re making an eternal difference. No matter where you find yourself today, be encouraged that you have meaning and potential! God wants to do a great work in your life.Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
